com.ibm.websphere.ras.annotation

Annotation Type Trivial


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD,TYPE,PACKAGE})
public @interface Trivial
    Indicates that a method or class is trivial to the point where instrumentation with diagnostic trace has no value. When used to annotate a class, all methods in the class are considered trivial. When used to annotate a package, all classes in the package are considered trivial.
